</dd>
          <dd class="break"></dd>
<dt id="section-2.12-1.7">Is it an advisory keyword or may it cause an automatic action:</dt>
          <dd id="section-2.12-1.8"> This keyword is advisory. Clients may show an icon to indicate to the user this was received via a masked email address - an alias created for a specific sender to hide the user's real email address.<a href="#section-2.12-1.8" class="pilcrow">¶</a>
</dd>
          <dd class="break"></dd>
<dt id="section-2.12-1.9">When/by whom the keyword is set/cleared:</dt>
